PropertyDetails.PublicRemarks: THE HOME YOU DESERVE   You'll love living in this quality 3 plus 1 bedroom bungalow that has been updated over the years with some unique and thoughtful touches.   Easy care hardwood floors encompass the entire main floor.  The open concept living room  / dining room has an over-sized sun filled front window with a great view of the front yard and covered front porch. These rooms are  tastefully complete, including the crown molding.  Just steps away is the recently renovated kitchen that features easy close drawers, ample counter-space and large pantry help make entertaining and daily family meals a true pleasure.   Enjoy cozy afternoons and evenings in the family room where there is a warming fireplace and sufficient space for the over-sized television, darts and entertaining. The 4th bedroom, 3 piece bath, laundry room and workshop round out the lower level. If you are in the market for a bungalow, close to all amenities including buses - call today! (id:19261)

Bedroom on Lower Level with bathroom
Lower level family room with gas fireplace

PropertyDetails.PublicRemarks: ELEGANT MASTERPIECE SERENELY LOCATED DIRECTLY BY THE OTTAWA RIVER, THIS PROPERTY WAS PLANNED WITH AN UNCOMPROMISING LEVEL OF QUALITY AND LUXURY. This splendid one acre lot with 283 feet of river front is fenced by professionally landscaped grounds with sprinkler system, natural fed pond and enhanced by a relaxing heated pool. The interior is equally magnificent. It reflects the meticulous care and attention to construction details using only the finest materials. The design of the kitchen deserves attention: numerous cabinets, granite counter tops, waste disposal, two sinks, top of the line appliances and wine fridge adjacent to a sunny eating area.  The large living room with fireplace is combined with the dining room which is of excellent size and will accommodate your numerous guests. Silk sheets are appropriate for the spacious master suite with private bathroom and well designed walk-in closet. A real gem! (square footage includes walk-out basement) (id:19261)

Building.HeatingType: Forced air, Hot water radiator heat

PropertyDetails.PublicRemarks: Super Spacious Bungalow backing on to farm land! This 3+1 bedroom/2 full bath has lots of updating done for you. The Master is very large with a huge walk-in closet and private en-suite bathroom. The second bedroom was originally two rooms, so offers tons of extra space. Third bedroom is located on the back of the house. The lower level is nice and bright with large windows, laminate flooring and a 4th bedroom.  This hamlet is located 20 minutes from the High Tech sector, Shopping, Golf and easy access to the 417. New propane furnace-2015, Air Cond 2013,  windows & doors 2011, new septic 2011, renovated bathroom 2016, updated kitchen with Stainless appliances. (id:19261)
